      <h1 style="text-align: center;font-family: alex brush;text-decoration:underline ; font-size:3.75rem ; padding-top: 3%;margin-bottom: 5%;color:#fe6402">Benefits of Waste Reduction</h1>
     <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card res-card">
          <img src="/images/energy-conservator.png" class="card-img-top benefits-image" alt="...">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 style="text-decoration: underline;color: #fe6402;">Resource Conservation</h3>
            <p class="card-text" style="margin-bottom: 5%;margin-top: 5%; font-size: 1.3rem;">Reducing waste preserves natural resources like forests, water, and minerals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card res-card">
          <img src="/images/green-energy.png" class="card-img-top benefits-image" alt="...">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 style="text-decoration: underline;color: #fe6402;">Energy Savings</h3>
            <p class="card-text" style="margin-bottom: 5%;margin-top: 5%; font-size: 1.3rem;"> Less waste means less energy used in manufacturing, reducing greenhouse gas emissions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card res-card">
          <img src="/images/net-zero.png" class="card-img-top benefits-image" alt="...">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 style="text-decoration: underline;color: #fe6402;">Emissions Reduction</h3>
            <p class="card-text" style="margin-bottom: 5%;margin-top: 5%; font-size: 1.3rem;">Waste reduction lowers emissions from landfilling and incineration, helping combat climate change.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card res-card">
          <img src="/images/earth.png" class="card-img-top benefits-image" alt="...">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 style="text-decoration: underline;color: #fe6402;">Ecosystem Protection</h3>
            <p class="card-text" style="margin-bottom: 5%;margin-top: 5%; font-size: 1.3rem;">By minimizing waste, we prevent pollution and protect wildlife and ecosystems.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card res-card">
          <img src="/images/prevent.png" class="card-img-top benefits-image" alt="...">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 style="text-decoration: underline;color: #fe6402;">Pollution Prevention</h3>
            <p class="card-text" style="margin-bottom: 5%;margin-top: 5%; font-size: 1.3rem;">Waste reduction reduces hazardous substances from entering the environment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card res-card">
          <img src="/images/landfill.png" class="card-img-top benefits-image" alt="...">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 style="text-decoration: underline;color: #fe6402;">Landfill Preservation</h3>
            <p class="card-text" style="margin-bottom: 5%;margin-top: 5%; font-size: 1.3rem;">Waste reduction extends the lifespan of existing landfills and reduces the need for new ones.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="but" style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="manage" ><button class="btn btn-primary" id="mnbtn" value="<%= data %>">Manage Your Waste</button></a>
    </div>
  </div>
    
      
  
  </div>
